name: Keiko Avi Demo
description: This is our first, self-produced Demo CD, designed to give you guys a little taste of the flavor that is Keiko Avi... ONLY 100 were produced, so your buying yourself a little slice of Keiko-history! Each CD was individually [and lovingly] designed by the band along with several of our closest man-chums. If you wanna select a specific cover, take a look at the selection on our myspace (www.myspace.com/keikoavi) in the photo album labelled "DEMO-art?!". It will tell you what number it is and who designed it, so just add a little note saying what number you would like and we'll do our best to see you get it! (smiley face.. lol)
